    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality example that has been pampered since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like finish with zero scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin smells fresh and the leather upholstery remains supple and free of any wear or creasing. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, with a smooth engine and crisp shifting, backed by a comprehensive service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a car that looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership.",
